# Puppet Duplicity

Install duplicity and quickly setup complete system backup to amazon s3 or rackspace

## Variables

1. $cfn_backup_action is either backup, restore, or none
2. $cfn_file_dest Amazon S3 Bucket Name
3. $cfn_access_id (aws access key id)
4. $cfn_secret_key (aws_secret_access_key)
5. files/backup-filelist.txt
	A newline separated list of files and directories to backup

## Setup

1. Install the module
2. Set your variables
3. Include duplicity
